description:

name: 2014 Kiwiana Illustrated Wall Calendar
description:
Please be aware of postage delays over the Christmas period, you can email me prior to purchase if you have any questions :)

Inspired by the "Cats Let Nothing Roar" calendar by Noa Bembibre, I wanted to create a Kiwi hommage to this great piece incorporating some of my little illustrations. Following the idea of Bembibre, each month in the calendar is a quirky sentence incorporating the name of the month, but with a kiwi twist. 

The calendar size is 200mm x 297mm, and is printed digitally on beautiful heavy textured 300gsm uncoated card. It is wire bound and comes with a hanging hook.

Calendars are safely posted in Rigid Envelopes.
